386→                        <div id="content">Let $x_1,\ldots,x_n$ be a sequence of distinct real numbers. Determine\[\max\left(\sum x_{i_r}\right),\]where the maximum is taken over all monotonic subsequences.</div>
387→                        <div id="problem_id"><a href="/1026">#1026</a>: <a href="#cite-Er71-1026" onclick="event.preventDefault();addNewBox('Er71','1026'); return false;">[Er71,p.107]</a></div>
